{"tid":454741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[失敗主義] 加泰: 獨立的代價","createTime":"2017-11-01T12:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T13:56:55.000Z","uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"405eb009ae7c481155ef6de10d2e80443610ae64","tid":454741,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"- 馬德里政府估計今次獨立風波對加泰地區做成二千五百億美元嘅損失.<br />\n- 巴塞羅那總商會對下年嘅加泰經濟增長預測由2.7％下調至2.5％.<br />\n- 當地商業機構估計加泰地區旅遊業會下跌兩成.<br />\n- 近期巴塞羅那酒店入住率跌至近八成.<br />\n- 西班牙地產網站創辦人指巴塞羅那南部嘅求售樓宇多咗五成.<br />\n<br />\nThe government in Madrid has been talking up the damage the separatists have caused to the region's $250 billion economy, one that's so intertwined with the rest of Spain.<br />\n<br />\nBarcelona&rsquo;s Chamber of Commerce cut its growth estimates for Catalonia to 2.5 percent from 2.7 percent for next year. Tourism may fall by about 20 percent, according to business group Aecoc, which represents more than 28,000 companies. Hotel occupancy rates in Barcelona fell to about 80 percent as tourists thought twice before booking, a local trade association said last week.<br />\n<br />\nForeign buyers have slowed down the purchase of real estate in Catalonia and the level of property for sale has increased by about 50 percent in some popular tourist beach destinations south of Barcelona, said Fernando Encinar, a co-founder of Idealista, Spain&rsquo;s largest property website.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-01/divided-and-conquered-catalonia-weighs-the-damage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2017-11-01%2Fdivided-and-conquered-catalonia-weighs-the-damage&d=%2BfX43UecHCvI3dkyCsNwuf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e02767a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-01/divided-and-conquered-catalonia-weighs-the-damage</a>"},{"pid":"442be20ae1f5029c7ac2976714840c974e6b84cf","tid":454741,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>- 馬德里政府估計今次獨立風波對加泰地區做成二千五百億美元嘅損失.<br />\n- 巴塞羅那總商會對下年嘅加泰經濟增長預測由2.7％下調至2.5％.<br />\n- 當地商業機構估計加泰地區旅遊業會下跌兩成.<br />\n- 近期巴塞羅那酒店入住率跌至近八成.<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">西班牙地產網站創辦人指巴塞羅那南部嘅求售樓宇多咗五成</span>.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87036279185b33d5ab448a0651c3bb7a7c8f9de1","tid":454741,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>- 馬德里政府估計今次獨立風波對加泰地區做成二千五百億美元嘅損失.<br />\n- 巴塞羅那總商會對下年嘅加泰經濟增長預測由2.7％下調至2.5％.<br />\n- 當地商業機構估計加泰地區旅遊業會下跌兩成.<br />\n- 近期巴塞羅那酒店入住率跌至近八成.<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">西班牙地產網站創辦人指巴塞羅那南部嘅求售樓宇多咗五成</span>.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n100萬港紙有無交易？"},{"pid":"3aedcaaf54e8e58f289c616c44eb6220ebf79ef3","tid":454741,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"馬德里政府估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b799af42d5466cdb5956e2d0c2f7e897a1ba6f","tid":454741,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬德里政府估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁巴塞總商會自己講經濟會冇咁好, 又信唔信? 係咪又要話商人都係建制唔會撐獨立?"},{"pid":"af2e4aeb1eafec2d97cb09419b679c6229a74b3d","tid":454741,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬德里政府估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8cbde03a5ea2b4b7f7b3b3a8c4b18921b6b6140d","tid":454741,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> </blockquote><br />\n咁都比你揾到位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ff7b2565faa3070d7c47620658e470347e3b58","tid":454741,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"去加泰叫雞會唔會平左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d8979cac4ae781b08305e70c83da8adff394eb","tid":454741,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> </blockquote><br />\n咁都比你揾到位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知我幾時會上榜.<br />\n<br />\n依排唔講加泰唔通講下屆區議會選舉咩?"},{"pid":"f14915b279e8d956d51158c07a4d6196e080bcd4","tid":454741,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"不如加泰招外國人入藉啦 我想買到屋"},{"pid":"d3ebed51737160d49989680b870b31208276b2a4","tid":454741,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"704986ea8654588e46bc1cd4f5f8cc77efb55692","tid":454741,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> </blockquote><br />\n咁都比你揾到位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知我幾時會上榜.<br />\n<br />\n依排唔講加泰唔通講下屆區議會選舉咩?</blockquote><br />\n講佢哋唔想見個野=五毛"},{"pid":"9339c7cd9488f166a281fa6f43668fde1fcbef65","tid":454741,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇，損失比想像中細<br />\n經濟增長預計只調低0.2%<br />\n入住率係跌至8成又唔係跌左8成<br />\n求售樓宇多一半都唔係好大件事<br />\n最大獲既係企業搬走，但睇黎大家都信加獨應該告一段落</blockquote><br />\n換個角度睇，損失咁細證明獨立運動收皮收得好快下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f48d4b59d34e95518d58dc60834bfd6a265aad","tid":454741,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> </blockquote><br />\n咁都比你揾到位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知我幾時會上榜.<br />\n<br />\n依排唔講加泰唔通講下屆區議會選舉咩?</blockquote><br />\n講佢哋唔想見個野=五毛</blockquote><br />\n失敗主義，好似係"},{"pid":"24847e8e6d6a04949c50038822e127936d94174c","tid":454741,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"無野既, 過多幾年再搞過<br />\n睇返歷史, 加秦獨立都搞左唔止一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bc4659591f922a6fd233d9d94b25a6e5a79fa6","tid":454741,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主專開加泰POST</strong></span> </blockquote><br />\n咁都比你揾到位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知我幾時會上榜.<br />\n<br />\n依排唔講加泰唔通講下屆區議會選舉咩?</blockquote><br />\n講佢哋唔想見個野=五毛</blockquote><br />\n失敗主義，好似係</blockquote><br />\n是日活躍五毛=加泰"},{"pid":"17d5fbfdf7e74fa6b1474a22a3401aa49485bc1c","tid":454741,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇，損失比想像中細<br />\n經濟增長預計只調低0.2%<br />\n入住率係跌至8成又唔係跌左8成<br />\n求售樓宇多一半都唔係好大件事<br />\n最大獲既係企業搬走，但睇黎大家都信加獨應該告一段落</blockquote><br />\n搬走咗嘅話唔會即刻搬番嚟, 你話死唔死先. 好彩仲未搬果啲就話局勢穩定中, 費事搞咁多嘢了.<br />\n<br />\nHundreds of companies left Catalonia by shifting their legal bases to ensure they wouldn't come under the auspices of a new Catalan Republic. Among them was CaixaBank SA, the largest bank in the region. The Caixa Group owns stakes in companies including the former Spanish phone monopoly Telefonica SA, oil producer Repsol SA and energy distributor Gas Natural SDG SA. <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We didn't decide to move to Madrid overnight and we won't decide to go back to Catalonia overnight,&rdquo; said Carlos Buesa, chairman of the biopharmaceutical company Oryzon Genomics SA, which announced the decision to move its headquarters from the Catalan to the Spanish capital on Oct. 3.<br />\n<br />\nIn one sign of a slow reversal, Freixenet SA, the maker of the sparkling wine cava, decided to keep its headquarters in Catalonia as a result of the Spanish government's move to seize control of the region. <br />\n<br />\nJordi Alberich, director general of Barcelona-based business association Cercle d&rsquo;Economia, said the hope is that economy will start to put the events behind it.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Walking around Barcelona, the atmosphere is very different from what it was last week,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;The hope is that the economic situation can start returning to something like normality.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4f628717da43005c2a2defda1d3fd14755c30f3f","tid":454741,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80e331d21189a2ce23316fc940a035aba5382d11","tid":454741,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇，損失比想像中細<br />\n經濟增長預計只調低0.2%<br />\n入住率係跌至8成又唔係跌左8成<br />\n求售樓宇多一半都唔係好大件事<br />\n最大獲既係企業搬走，但睇黎大家都信加獨應該告一段落</blockquote><br />\n換個角度睇，損失咁細證明獨立運動收皮收得好快下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，呢個就係我想表達既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前仲吹到中國無咗香港就玩完咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aacbf05ab1f60582d3abd968b17d9e4c8cbc06c","tid":454741,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"樓主我同你講啊  佢依D死人list  補選前成日見架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707b25becfe6f3c88bd4289ea1e7b347d521f192","tid":454741,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"晌十月嘅西班牙新增失業人口中, 加泰佔超過四份一.<br />\n<br />\nEvidence emerged Friday of the possible economics strains caused by the crisis. Catalonia accounted for more than a quarter of the increase of 56,844 in the number of Spaniards newly registered as unemployed in October."},{"pid":"74af7eb06f61aef55e599b7c4c99954a6344a666","tid":454741,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">個人簽名<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我喺時事台整條五毛list以正視聽屌你老母連生你就搬去站務台，你咁搞咩意思啊？我屌你老母五毛「民國復興」bam完又復出又係咩意思啊？<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家五毛改名扮其他人講嘢，明顯係離間分化策略，連生你郁都唔郁下佢地！</span>頂你個肺連生竟然殺忠良不殺奸臣！屌你老母仆街冚家鏟連生包庇五毛，助紂為虐！為虎作倀！天理不容！<br />\n<br />\n我正大光明！做嘅所有嘢全部都係想杜絕五毛！你連狗兼成班濕鳩契弟管理員，竟然夠膽移走我地對抗五毛嘅post！反而民國復興，三色貓，JR嗰班五毛又唔ban走！助他人志氣滅自己威風！我話你聽死連狗你再咁搞落去連登只會步高登後塵比五毛完全攻陷！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（請廣傳）<br />\n五毛/假膠一律統稱支那人<br />\n<br />\n假膠唔係五毛，但就做緊五毛一樣嘅事，以前大事大非面前絕對唔會玩嘢，但宜家佢地咩時候都仲扮鬼扮馬，搞到分唔清邊個打邊個，佢地已經走火入魔，所以喺以後逢見假膠請一律認作五毛處理<br />\n<br />\n由於支那人再次泛濫，現列出部分人渣名錄，比大家留意返相關人渣，如有遺漏希望大家增補，對抗支那人一齊努力<br />\n<br />\n最新名錄(定期更新)：<br />\n毛澤東 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #90863<br />\n三色貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #466